### Contact Manager API — HTTP Test File
### Dùng với VSCode REST Client extension hoặc IntelliJ HTTP Client
### Thay @baseUrl và @apiKey trước khi dùng

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@apiKey = g-YDfJ-lOemAuZ10Qi6UmEcvKyUVVpEA-XVnNq3gLTY

# ─── Health ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

# ─── Contacts — List & Search ─────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Danh sách contacts (50 đầu tiên)
GET {{baseUrl}}/contacts
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Tìm theo tên (prefix search)
GET {{baseUrl}}/contacts?search=nguyen
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Tìm theo organization
GET {{baseUrl}}/contacts?search=acme
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Filter theo category
GET {{baseUrl}}/contacts?category=myContacts
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Filter theo email domain
GET {{baseUrl}}/contacts?domain=gmail.com
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Filter theo email cụ thể
GET {{baseUrl}}/contacts?email=user@gmail.com
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Filter theo userDefined key
GET {{baseUrl}}/contacts?udKey=github.token
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Filter có userDefined
GET {{baseUrl}}/contacts?hasUD=true
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Phân trang — trang 2 (dùng nextCursor từ response trước)
GET {{baseUrl}}/contacts?cursor=CURSOR_FROM_PREVIOUS_RESPONSE&limit=50
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Sort theo displayName
GET {{baseUrl}}/contacts?sort=displayName&order=asc
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Combo: category + udKey
GET {{baseUrl}}/contacts?category=myContacts&udKey=github.token
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

# ─── Contacts — Detail ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Xem chi tiết 1 contact
GET {{baseUrl}}/contacts/uid_I12Rd9qMPPPl
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

# ─── Contacts — Create ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Tạo contact mới (wrapped format)
POST {{baseUrl}}/contacts
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contact": {
    "displayName": "Nguyen Van An",
    "emails": [
      { "type": ["INTERNET", "WORK"], "value": "an@company.com" },
      { "type": ["INTERNET", "HOME"], "value": "vanan@gmail.com" }
    ],
    "phones": [
      { "type": ["CELL"], "value": "0901234567" }
    ],
    "organization": "ACME Corp",
    "categories": ["myContacts"]
  },
  "userDefined": {
    "github.token": "ghp_xxxxxxxxxxxx",
    "gitea.token": "gta_xxxxxxxxxxxx"
  }
}

### Tạo contact mới (flat format)
POST {{baseUrl}}/contacts
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "displayName": "Jane Smith",
  "emails": [{ "value": "jane@example.com" }]
}

# ─── Contacts — Update ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Update toàn bộ (PUT)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/contacts/uid_abc123
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contact": {
    "displayName": "Nguyen Van An (Updated)",
    "emails": [
      { "type": ["INTERNET", "WORK"], "value": "an.new@company.com" }
    ],
    "phones": [{ "type": ["CELL"], "value": "0909999999" }],
    "organization": "New Corp",
    "categories": ["myContacts", "work"]
  },
  "userDefined": {
    "github.token": "ghp_new_token"
  }
}

### Update từng phần (PATCH)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/contacts/uid_abc123
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contact": {
    "organization": "Updated Org"
  },
  "userDefined": {
    "slack.token": "xoxb-new-token"
  }
}

# ─── Contacts — Delete ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Xóa contact
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/contacts/uid_abc123
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

# ─── Lookup ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Lookup theo email
GET {{baseUrl}}/contacts/by-email/user@gmail.com
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Lookup theo email có ký tự đặc biệt (URL encode)
GET {{baseUrl}}/contacts/by-email/user%40gmail.com
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Lookup theo userDefined key
GET {{baseUrl}}/contacts/by-ud-key/github.token
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Liệt kê tất cả userDefined keys
GET {{baseUrl}}/contacts/ud-keys
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

# ─── Bulk ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Bulk import (async)
POST {{baseUrl}}/contacts/bulk/import
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contacts": [
    {
      "contact": {
        "displayName": "Contact 1",
        "emails": [{ "value": "c1@example.com" }]
      }
    },
    {
      "contact": {
        "displayName": "Contact 2",
        "emails": [{ "value": "c2@example.com" }]
      }
    }
  ],
  "sourceFile": "manual_import"
}

### Kiểm tra trạng thái import job
GET {{baseUrl}}/contacts/bulk/import/job_JOBID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Export toàn bộ (JSON)
GET {{baseUrl}}/contacts/bulk/export
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Export category cụ thể (VCF)
GET {{baseUrl}}/contacts/bulk/export?format=vcf&category=myContacts
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Export với limit
GET {{baseUrl}}/contacts/bulk/export?limit=1000
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

# ─── Meta ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Thống kê tổng
GET {{baseUrl}}/contacts/meta/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
